# Per-run open_prep dashboard outputs (timestamped HTML/CSV/JSON snapshots
# produced by `python -m open_prep …` and the streamlit dashboard runs).
# These accumulate without bound on contributor machines and CI hosts and
# show up as ever-growing untracked drift in `git status`. They are not
# part of the canonical artifact corpus.
